<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink318">
<l>āynalam pacappa varumpaṭar naliya</l>
<l>vēymaruḷ paṇaittōḷ villiḻai nekiḻa</l>
<l>nacainaṉi koṉṟōr maṉṟa vicainimirn</l>
<l>tōṭeri naṭanta vaippiṟ</l>
<l>kōṭuyar piṟaṅkaṉ malaiyiṟan tōrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who has traversed the lofty mountains with tall peaks, </l>
<l>in the region where running fire spreads with loud crackle – </l>
<l>Alas! – he completely killed love [for him], </l>
<l>as my fine beauty has paled, I suffer from great anguish,  </l>
<l>and bright jewels slip from my thick shoulders, resembling bamboo.  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
